    <p>
      I have spent the better part of my career deep in <strong>cyber security</strong> and <strong>fraud prevention</strong>. From building Self-Sovereign Identity infrastructure at Tangle Labs — where I led tech on NGDIL, a UNESCO project that became the reference SSI demo and won multiple awards — to architecting end-to-end fraud prevention software for trade and supply chain at Ensombl. Cryptography, trust systems, and making sure bad actors can't game the system is what gets me out of bed in the morning.
